OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FA group of Carlisle United fans are
OL,8,Fcycling to one of English football's
OL,9,Flongest ever away games.
OL,11,FThey'll be pedalling more than 500
OL,12,Fmiles from Cumbria all the way to
OL,13,FCornwall for United's penultimate game
OL,14,Fof the regular season at Truro City in
OL,15,Faid of Cancer Research UK and the MND
OL,16,FAssociation.
OL,18,FIt was a decision made at the pub in
OL,19,FJune 2025, a group called 'Truro or
OL,20,FBust' was created.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
