PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775664666
OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FBrian Haughan said: "It was a probably
OL,8,Fa daft idea we had, one night we where
OL,9,Fout drinking and we came up with this
OL,10,Fstupid idea to cycle to Truro."
OL,12,FThey are planning on leaving Saturday
OL,13,F11 from Brunton Park, the 525 mile
OL,14,Fjourney will take seven days, with the
OL,15,Fchallenge raising money for two
OL,16,Fcharities close to their hearts:
OL,17,FCancer Research and Motor Neurone
OL,18,FDisease Association.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775664666
OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"One of the lads doing it, his mam
OL,8,Fdied of MND, and my aunt has MND as
OL,9,Fwell, so we thought that was a good
OL,10,Fidea to do it," Brian explained.
OL,12,FHe also said the group has friends and
OL,13,Ffamily who have died of cancer too.
OL,15,FBrian told ITV Border: "The money
OL,16,Fhopefully goes a long way to curing
OL,17,Fand awareness towards these diseases.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
