PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775664666
OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"It affects everyone really at some
OL,8,Ftime in your life, especially cancer.
OL,9,FAnd then MND, it seems to be more and
OL,10,Fmore so any awareness is good."
OL,12,FIan Shaw, is another member of the
OL,13,Ftrio cycling and said: "It's made even
OL,14,Fmore difficult, by the fact that none
OL,15,Fof us are cyclists, we're all just
OL,16,Fnormal blokes and thought we'd give it
OL,17,Fa go."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
