PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775664666
OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FThey've been training for the last six
OL,8,Fmonths, and say an unexpected benefit
OL,9,Fhas come: "We've been dropping a few
OL,10,Fpounds here and there, and just
OL,11,Fgetting used to being in the saddle."
OL,13,FCarlisle play Truro away on the
OL,14,FSaturday 18, for a 15:00 kick-off, the
OL,15,FCornish side are currently sat at the
OL,16,Fbottom of the National League.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
