OL,3,C'It was a daft idea' - Carlisle FC
OL,4,Cfans to cycle to Truro match for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FIan said: "Hopefully we get the win.
OL,8,FCement that third position in the
OL,9,Fleague. Obviously a little bit sad for
OL,10,FTruro having just come up, it looks
OL,11,Flike they're heading straight back
OL,12,Fdown. We still want to get the win."
